{{Respond|minus|{{{1|Closing without action}}}|alt=no}}<noinclude>{{documentation|content={{Template:Resolved mark/doc |type=checkmark|where=at [[Wikipedia:Sockpuppet investigations]] to indicate that a case has been reviewed and determined to not be actionable. |para=The template accepts a single parameter (unnamed or given as {{para|1}}) that changes the phrase "Closing without action" to the text specified in the parameter. {{pb}}{{tlx|cwa}} may be used as a shortcut.}}}}
